>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-07-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/staging-an-art-festival-at-one-of-jerusalems-most-volatile-sites/00000190-a20f-d03e-a5fd-bbbfee850000</guid></item><item><title>“我们失败了”：以色列军队向贝埃里基布兹居民展示 10 月 7 日的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-beeri-residents-say-critical-questions-remain-unanswered-after-oct-7-army-probe/00000190-a214-dd20-abfa-fe1732640000</link><description>居民们表示，“可以说调查很彻底”，但补充说，关键问题没有得到解答。他们现在呼吁成立一个国家调查委员会，“不遗余力”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 14:14:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-beeri-residents-say-critical-questions-remain-unanswered-after-oct-7-army-probe/00000190-a214-dd20-abfa-fe1732640000</guid></item><item><title>难怪以色列右翼认为左翼想要杀死内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-no-wonder-the-israeli-right-thinks-the-left-wants-to-kill-netanyahu/00000190-a147-dd20-abfa-ff57efa70000</link><description>右翼担心左翼分子可能会暗杀首相，这只不过是那些除了暴力之外不接受任何解决方案的人的典型预测。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 12:29:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-no-wonder-the-israeli-right-thinks-the-left-wants-to-kill-netanyahu/00000190-a147-dd20-abfa-ff57efa70000</guid></item><item><title>为了达成人质协议，以色列必须解决其对拉法和埃及-加沙边境的控制问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/to-reach-a-hostage-deal-israel-must-address-its-control-of-rafah-and-egypt-gaza-border/00000190-a109-ddf1-abb6-edc90af90000</link><description>埃及要求以色列从加沙边境撤军，并要求巴勒斯坦权力机构管理加沙的过境点，而以色列则要求确保国际部队能够在脆弱的人质谈判中监督加沙-埃及边境</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/to-reach-a-hostage-deal-israel-must-address-its-control-of-rafah-and-egypt-gaza-border/00000190-a109-ddf1-abb6-edc90af90000</guid></item><item><title>获救的以色列人质起诉在加沙雇佣巴勒斯坦人质的美国非营利组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-sues-u-s-non-profit-that-employed-palestinian-captor-in-gaza/00000190-9c81-d07e-a798-beb136350000</link><description>该诉讼称，该组织的领导人“故意并故意获取和传播哈马斯的宣传”，并“物质上支持”哈马斯的恐怖主义行为</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:15:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-sues-u-s-non-profit-that-employed-palestinian-captor-in-gaza/00000190-9c81-d07e-a798-beb136350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列计划征召的极端正统人士远远不能满足军队当前的需求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-planned-draft-of-ultra-orthodox-falls-far-short-of-the-armys-current-needs/00000190-9e56-d41c-abfc-def65b770000</link><description>根据正在制定的计划，两年内将招募约 9,600 名年轻的正统派男子——远少于 63,000 名处于征兵年龄的极端正统男子。只要加沙战争持续下去，总参谋部将继续依靠预备役军人，而且在未来几年边境预计紧张的时期也是如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-planned-draft-of-ultra-orthodox-falls-far-short-of-the-armys-current-needs/00000190-9e56-d41c-abfc-def65b770000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，随着卡塔尔休战谈判即将恢复，哈马斯可能在“几天内”达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-hamas-deal-possible-within-days-as-qatar-truce-talks-set-to-resume/00000190-9ef8-dfb2-a799-befd66de0000</link><description>国防部长约夫·加兰特：“现在实现我们的道德义务并将人质带回家的机会有限”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-hamas-deal-possible-within-days-as-qatar-truce-talks-set-to-resume/00000190-9ef8-dfb2-a799-befd66de0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在无人机袭击北部地区受重伤；以色列谈判代表从卡塔尔返回</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article-live/u-s-cautiously-optimistic-about-gaza-cease-fire-as-sides-head-to-qatar-for-talks/00000190-9fa1-dfb2-a799-bff5e84c0000</link><description>《华盛顿邮报》报道，以色列和哈马斯一致认为，在可能的人质交易第二阶段中，双方都不会统治加沙。人质协议，风险是可以克服的 ■ 纳斯鲁拉：如果以色列和哈马斯达成加沙休战，黎巴嫩战斗将立即停止 ■ 以色列国防军表示，它袭击了突破两国边境缓冲区的叙利亚军队目标 ■ 以色列命令加沙城的所有巴勒斯坦人向南部撤离随着战斗的加剧</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article-live/u-s-cautiously-optimistic-about-gaza-cease-fire-as-sides-head-to-qatar-for-talks/00000190-9fa1-dfb2-a799-bff5e84c0000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派拉比领袖指示学生无视以色列军队征召令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/leading-ultra-orthodox-rabbi-instructs-students-to-ignore-israeli-army-call-up-orders/00000190-9f8d-d962-a3b7-9fbf3f350001</link><description>以色列立陶宛极端正统派社区领袖拉比多夫·兰多 (Rabbi Dov Lando) 写道，“法院已向托拉世界宣战”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:15:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/leading-ultra-orthodox-rabbi-instructs-students-to-ignore-israeli-army-call-up-orders/00000190-9f8d-d962-a3b7-9fbf3f350001</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方知道在准备极端正统征兵时必须谨慎行事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-knows-it-must-tread-carefully-as-it-prepares-for-the-ultra-orthodox-draft/00000190-9dfb-dbad-adfc-fdfbbc8e0000</link><description>以色列国防军计划征召在职和退学的犹太学院学生，并打算赋予拉比对新兵服役的监督权</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 23:25:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-knows-it-must-tread-carefully-as-it-prepares-for-the-ultra-orthodox-draft/00000190-9dfb-dbad-adfc-fdfbbc8e0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：内塔尼亚胡办公室试图更改以色列内阁战时会议纪要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/report-netanyahus-bureau-tried-to-alter-minutes-of-war-time-meetings-of-israeli-cabinet/00000190-9ea1-dfb2-a799-bef5354e0000</link><d