>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/u-s-intelligence-accuses-iran-of-mobilizing-pro-palestinian-protesters-in-america/00000190-9d77-ddf1-abb6-fdf789160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列没有赢得加沙战争。它的其他战争也没有那么成功</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-not-won-the-gaza-war-its-other-wars-werent-so-successful-either/00000190-9caf-da1a-adf0-9ebfc5720000</link><description>历史上第二长的战争已经过去九个月了，以色列是否擅长战争是一个令人烦恼的问题，并提出了巨大的问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 17:24:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-not-won-the-gaza-war-its-other-wars-werent-so-successful-either/00000190-9caf-da1a-adf0-9ebfc5720000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡如何系统性地挫败哈马斯释放人质的谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-timeline/.premium/how-netanyahu-has-systematically-foiled-talks-to-release-hostages-from-hamas-captivity/00000190-9b91-d591-a7ff-fff341120000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 17:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-timeline/.premium/how-netanyahu-has-systematically-foiled-talks-to-release-hostages-from-hamas-captivity/00000190-9b91-d591-a7ff-fff341120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 278 天：内塔尼亚胡表示，如果不跨越“红线”，他承诺停战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-278-netanyahu-says-committed-to-truce-if-it-doesnt-cross-red-lines/00000190-9d7f-dbad-adfc-fdff54ad0001</link><description>由摩萨德负责人率领的以色列代表团前往卡塔尔参加休战峰会，参与峰会的官员称其为“决定性的”。 ■ 人质家属踏上从耶路撒冷前往特拉维夫的为期三天的游行。 ■ 加沙的报道称，以色列对流离失所者营地的袭击造成 29 人死亡，主要是妇女和儿童 ■ 以色列国防军表示，约有 30 枚火箭从黎巴嫩发射到以色列北部 ■ 战争进入 278 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:45:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-278-netanyahu-says-committed-to-truce-if-it-doesnt-cross-red-lines/00000190-9d7f-dbad-adfc-fdff54ad0001</guid></item><item><title>真主党在以色列深处拍摄的最可怕的教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-10/ty-article/up-to-date-aerial-intel-the-scariest-lesson-from-hezbollahs-footage-of-inside-israel/00000190-9cf9-d41c-abfc-defd5de40000</link><description>无人机镜头显示真主党拥有有效打击的实时情报。文章发表数小时后，火箭弹袭击了所示基地之一，造成两名以色列平民死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-10/ty-article/up-to-date-aerial-intel-the-scariest-lesson-from-hezbollahs-footage-of-inside-israel/00000190-9cf9-d41c-abfc-defd5de40000</guid></item></channel></rss>